name: MQIslamicPrayerTimes
summary: Sunset is the time of day when our sky meets the outer space solar winds. There are blue, pink, and purple swirls
description: spinning and twisting, like clouds of balloons caught in a blender. The sun moves slowly to hide behind the line of horizon, while the moon races to take its place in prominence atop the night sky. People slow to a crawl, entranced, fully forgetting the deeds that still must be done. There is a coolness, a calmness, when the sun does set.
